freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: This past week, foods that I eat regularly have led to a tingling sensation and slight swelling in my palate, and lips.  Examples of the food are bbq Turkey, a chicken wrap, cereal with yogurt, berries and walnuts.  I have not had that happen before.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Mild:  My olfaction seemed to be slightly off last night, but was fine today.
